Bruno Lochet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruno_Lochet 0 Bruno Lochet (born 18 October 1959) is a French actor. He is best known for playing in the cult TV series Les Deschiens (1993-2002), in which he played alongside Yolande Moreau. Bruno_Lochet ( born_18_October_1959 ) is a_French_actor .
